明立場啦，唔通真係咁把炮放棄成個中國市場咩。戴番個頭盔先，我呢就唔知咁多，唔知間公司政治立場係乜。我淨系知有好多手足打緊呢間公司工，本身市道都差你咁搞一搞一陣成班手足冇工開。間公司而家就出左通告叫我地唔好再答任何關於政治立場既問題，所以就算你落鋪問我地任何一個關於自己立場既野，我地都唔答得你。但你要知道，我地好多人除左件制服，都可能係係條街上面派過水比你既手足，亦都可能係蒙面既英雄。"},{"pid":"15c765f6567c03d2ded2a9edc3f1e32e5d2d4d9c","tid":2180272,"uid":157054,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本唔好用 舊電又廢<br />\n係我老母中意買"},{"pid":"f12c49505663a01b8ff1ec8decff3aba97475955","tid":2180272,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"15c765f6567c03d2ded2a9edc3f1e32e5d2d4d9c","tid":2180272,"uid":157054,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本唔好用 舊電又廢<br />\n係我老母中意買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:03:00.000Z","msg":"聽講個摩打好快打柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e4c91363cd9cc544e2dd8c8e6811ac00e18ec8","tid":2180272,"uid":157054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f12c49505663a01b8ff1ec8decff3aba97475955","tid":2180272,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"15c765f6567c03d2ded2a9edc3f1e32e5d2d4d9c","tid":2180272,"uid":157054,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本唔好用 舊電又廢<br />\n係我老母中意買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:03:00.000Z","msg":"聽講個摩打好快打柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"屋企有風扇 壞過兩次又細風 垃圾"},{"pid":"5e4ac486d6a6aaac8db7b77be32e26ca89c8e499","tid":2180272,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0e4c91363cd9cc544e2dd8c8e6811ac00e18ec8","tid":2180272,"uid":157054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f12c49505663a01b8ff1ec8decff3aba97475955","tid":2180272,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor